 insight into whether the representation or the regression model determines\nthe overall model performance, nine ML models obtained by combining the\nrepresentations and regression models of the top three approaches were compared\nby looking at the correlations among prediction errors. At fixed\nrepresentation, the largest correlation is observed in predictions made with\nkernel ridge regression and neural network, reflecting a similar performance on\nthe same test set samples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2018 22:55:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-25"}
