inner vesicle\nwhen the inner vesicle is a solid inclusion. Additionally a very elaborate\nphase diagram is presented in the modified viscosity-shear rate parameter\nspace, which could be tested in future experiments or numerical simulations\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Dec 2018 07:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-04"}
